706935f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sumpter Street - Saratoga Avenue
706935f-a.text:
Sumpter Street, at, adjoining and west of the S.W. corner of Saratoga
Ave. At the laft of the Hebrew Educational Center, is a 4-story frame houee,
No. 180 Saratoga Ave.
April 29, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
